
'''西蒙·R·F·普莱斯'''（{{lang-en|Simon Rowland Francis Price}}，{{bd|1954年|9月27日|2011年|6月14日}}）是一位[[英国|英国]]的[[罗马史|罗马史]][[历史学家|历史学家]]，专攻古罗马[[宗教史|宗教史]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=North |first1=John |title=Simon Price obituary |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2011/aug/21/simon-price-obituary |website=The Guardian |date=2011-08-21 |access-date=2021-02-18 |archive-date=2018-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004042527/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2011/aug/21/simon-price-obituary |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主要作品有《古希腊人的宗教生活》（''Religions of the Ancient Greeks''）、《罗马人的宗教》（''Religions of Rome''，与[[玛丽·比尔德|玛丽·比尔德]]等人合著）<ref name="BeardNorth1998">{{cite book|author1=Mary Beard|author2=John North|author3=Simon Price|title=Religions of Rome: Volume 2, A Sourcebook|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UFzcAwAAQBAJ|date=28 June 1998|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-316-13919-6|access-date=2021-02-18|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812013031/https://books.google.com/books?id=UFzcAwAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《古典欧洲的诞生：从特洛伊到奥古斯丁》（''The Birth of Classical Europe: The History of Troy to Augustine''，与彼得·索恩曼合著）<ref name="PriceThonemann2011">{{cite book|author1=Simon Price|author2=Peter Thonemann|title=The Birth of Classical Europe: A History from Troy to Augustine|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1Q-s9CbuCQgC|date=17 February 2011|publisher=Penguin Publishing Group|isbn=978-1-101-47579-9|access-date=2021-02-18|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125131447/https://books.google.com/books?id=1Q-s9CbuCQgC|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。

